In your source file, the etaMax is  related to scalar ：

const ScalarType stress_delta = effective_trial_stress - (_three_shear_modulus * scalar);
const ScalarType etaMax = _etaM0 * std::exp(_mvM * stress_delta);

but in computeDerivative , when calculating the creep_rate_derivative, you didn't consider the derivation of etaMax with respect to scalar  :

const GenericReal<is_ad> creep_rate_derivative =
-(std::sqrt(2/3)) *   1/(2etaMax) _three_shear_modulus;

